ygData.msgSnippet: Just checked the patch message and didn t see any word about it.  But they may not announce it...just like when they allowed warriors to get dual wield at 13
ygData.messageBody:
Just checked the patch message and didn't see any word about it. But they
may not announce it...just like when they allowed warriors to get dual wield
at 13 instead of 15. I met alot of warriors who at level 14 still hadn't
trained dual becuase they didn't know they could.

Bael
18th Level Tier'dal Warrior
